snippet: A former state investigator looking into Google’s Street View has identified the so-called Engineer Doe.
abstract: Former state investigator looking into uproar over Google's Street View identifies the so-called Engineer Doe who wrote the code as Marius Milner; Federal Communications Commission recently closed its inquiry into the project with a finding that Google broke no laws but had obstructed its investigation.

byline.original: By STEVE LOHR and DAVID STREITFELD

lead_paragraph: A former state investigator looking into Google’s Street View has identified the so-called Engineer Doe.

headline.seo: Engineer in Google’s Street View Is Identified
headline.main: Data Engineer in Google Case Is Identified
headline.print_headline: Data Engineer In Google Case Is Identified
